lesungsbegleitendes Textbuch an.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access. Unless otherwise specified individually in the content, the work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives (CC BY-NC-ND) license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Feb 2021) 0aColor (Philosophy). 0aColorxPsychological aspects. 0aPhilosophy (General). 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook Paket De Gruyter Ontos 2002-2012z9783110331219oZDB-23-DON0 cprintz978311032934640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110329476zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110329476zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110329476.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DONc2002d2012  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-GPHc2000d2014